openshot: OpenShot Video Editor is a free, open-source, non-linear video editor,
openshot: based on Python, GTK, and MLT. It can edit video and audio files,
openshot: composite and transition video files, and mix multiple layers of video
openshot: and audio together and  render the output in many different formats.
